where z0,c represents the residual vector of the c-th quantizer and qc(z0,c) denotes the closest entry in the c-th codebook.
3) Decoder: The decoder generates a raw waveform from

the audio codec yÀÜ = G(zq). We calculate a reconstruction loss Lrecon between the generated xÀÜmel and ground-truth Melspectrograms xmel to improve the training efficiency of the decoder. The reconstruction loss is defined as

Lrecon = ||xmel ‚àí xÀÜmel||1.

